{"tid":1285851,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"[求助] 新屋裝修咩都唔識 誠邀識裝修/有搬屋經驗既巴絲指教","createTime":"2019-07-04T16:59:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-04T18:58:24.000Z","uid":267300,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"fe553aa4daabb0e1ecb3d9a09661764017434945","tid":1285851,"uid":267300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T16:59:01.000Z","msg":"黎緊要搬新屋<br />\n我既朋友圈子無人曉裝修既野<br />\n親戚又愛莫能助<br />\n<br />\n我要一個人一腳踢搞吉屋好無助<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n希望有善良既巴絲可以幫手俾啲意見<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<br />\nBackground: <br />\n新單位，中層，200呎以下，位置近海多過近山，廚廁唔洗點執住<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n主要係牆同地下既問題 其他未諗到住：<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">1. 鋪地板</span><br />\n我問過唔同朋友既意見<br />\n得出三個答案：瓷磚、膠地板(長方形一塊要砌嗰啲)、無痕膠地板(一塊過鋪晒成間屋)<br />\n聽聞鋪磚係最襟用 但係成本最高<br />\n又有人話鋪一塊過嗰隻最方便唔洗煩<br />\n依家好猶豫唔知點處理地板問題⋯⋯<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">2. 油牆</span><br />\nBudget有限所以打算自己一腳踢<br />\n我睇過賣油漆既鋪 又乳膠漆又環保漆又乜好頭暈<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n想知應該要點選擇？(例如牌子/款)<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">3. 請槍vs DIY</span><br />\n想知道如果地板油牆呢啲外判俾師傅同自己做會差幾多<br />\n我擔心太大舊錢俾唔起 但自己落手又好無安全感<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">4. 額外工夫</span><br />\n我聽聞上漆前要線牆 鋪地板前要刎平個水泥地<br />\n想問以上步驟係咪必要？<br />\n如果係 要預幾錢左右<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">5. 冷氣機</span><br />\n全屋只係裝一部冷氣既話1匹夠唔夠做？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">如果識裝修既你見到<br />\n又唔介意我多野問可以留低tg指導下我<br />\n我會好感激你<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"120b154ca0de7e03a37ffc6d1b60209d7805ce2e","tid":1285851,"uid":181014,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T17:22:18.000Z","msg":"我無野講 <br />\nBtw 幫你推推"},{"pid":"d8bd8ca5dae08d44e45136637423cee9049acb0a","tid":1285851,"uid":34293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T17:25:16.000Z","msg":"間屋家陣係咩樣  影黎睇下"},{"pid":"88142ec692941a38404b8f770924ce6cb766db5a","tid":1285851,"uid":130140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T17:35:07.000Z","msg":"地板：如果你唔識搞就鋪一塊過嗰啲膠地板啦，又平，不過你間屋本身無地板嘅咩？<br />\n<br />\n油牆：如果你純粹為想轉色，就唔好搞咁多野，落五金鋪揀啱色油兩三層咪算囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />雖然摸落會有啲凹凹凸凸，但無所謂啦，當特色囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n冷氣：匹半就肯定夠涼，由其係如果間唔中有朋友上黎hea，或上黎打下邊爐咁<br />\n如果你唔會搞咁多野、唔會太多人上黎hea就一匹都夠"},{"pid":"61a26231512853a621608e8c46783c4d06caea89","tid":1285851,"uid":130140,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T17:40:39.000Z","msg":"如果間屋係買嘅，不如你努力格下價邊度搵人整最平啦，由其地板，因為如果你自己鋪磚，一下鋪得唔好冬天好易爆磚"},{"pid":"c5e3a4914c86ac67b5acb20239366faf6fb01e89","tid":1285851,"uid":112702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T17:43:23.000Z","msg":"建議鋪磚<br />\n果d口咩無痕膠地板唔好信<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b53302341ca88e3de26f82a20251deb670a40fc","tid":1285851,"uid":267300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d8bd8ca5dae08d44e45136637423cee9049acb0a","tid":1285851,"uid":34293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T17:25:16.000Z","msg":"間屋家陣係咩樣  影黎睇下"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T17:44:28.000Z","msg":"睇樓嗰陣影左幾張 但完全無參考價值<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8cf448b700ee5d2716381b8b01822a6be22d1579","tid":1285851,"uid":154533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T17:46:05.000Z","msg":"自己住實係鋪la<br />\n油漆不外乎 立邦 Ici用紅罐"},{"pid":"d0a64b99e04b4ceb0021c74480a8034b53a7cfeb","tid":1285851,"uid":267300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"88142ec692941a38404b8f770924ce6cb766db5a","tid":1285851,"uid":130140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T17:35:07.000Z","msg":"地板：如果你唔識搞就鋪一塊過嗰啲膠地板啦，又平，不過你間屋本身無地板嘅咩？<br />\n<br />\n油牆：如果你純粹為想轉色，就唔好搞咁多野，落五金鋪揀啱色油兩三層咪算囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />雖然摸落會有啲凹凹凸凸，但無所謂啦，當特色囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n冷氣：匹半就肯定夠涼，由其係如果間唔中有朋友上黎hea，或上黎打下邊爐咁<br />\n如果你唔會搞咁多野、唔會太多人上黎hea就一匹都夠"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T17:46:42.000Z","msg":"無地板架 係水泥地黎<br />\n我驚我9油好快就甩晒灰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd08b4f9c387249fd66686e73e10c46198a84469","tid":1285851,"uid":154533,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T17:46:56.000Z","msg":"你本身如果冇做開既 油油同地板唔好自己黎la 實後悔"},{"pid":"204630cb0798f9326e5cd231bf096656099e2156","tid":1285851,"uid":267300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c5e3a4914c86ac67b5acb20239366faf6fb01e89","tid":1285851,"uid":112702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T17:43:23.000Z","msg":"建議鋪磚<br />\n果d口咩無痕膠地板唔好信<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T17:48:54.000Z","msg":"Why<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />一塊過真係好L方便<br />\n但我覺得啲傢私一移位<br />\n塊爛鬼地膠就會有痕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91ca9d75c0729eccd67c3c4333854c29211dbddc","tid":1285851,"uid":154533,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T17:49:03.000Z","msg":"成間緊靠一部一匹機緊係唔夠la <br />\n聽你講既野 完全係門外漢0認識 唔建議自己搞  手尾隨時仲貴"},{"pid":"9a0b305a39eead5d091e0bfa3de900a988c506a6","tid":1285851,"uid":267300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dd08b4f9c387249fd66686e73e10c46198a84469","tid":1285851,"uid":15453